%N A373339 Number of permutations in symmetric group S_n with an even number of cycles of length 2 or more.
%F A373339 a(n) = n!/2 - (n-2)*2^(n-2) = A001710(n) - A036289(n-2).
%F A373339 a(n) = A000142(n) - A373340(n).
%F A373339 E.g.f.: (1/(1 - x) + exp(2*x)*(1 - x))/2. - _Stefano Spezia_, Jun 05 2024
%e A373339 a(1)=a(2)=a(3)=1 due to S_1,S_2,S_3 containing 1 permutation with an even number of non-fixed point cycles: the identity permutation, with 0 non-fixed point cycles.
%e A373339 a(4)=4 due to S_4 containing 4 permutations with an even number of non-fixed point cycles: the 3 (2,2)-cycles (12)(34),(13)(24),(14)(23); and the identity permutation (1)(2)(3)(4).
